obj_root_law:
  slug the-union-territory-goods-and-services-tax-act-2017
  handle (2252)
  collectionHandle 123456789/1362
  title `The Union Territory Goods and Services Tax Act, 2017`
  actNumber (14)
  enactmentDate 2017-04-12
  sourceUrl `https://www.indiacode.nic.in/handle/123456789/2252`
  sources obj_root_law_sources
  sections obj_root_law_sections
  hindiTitle `संघ राज्‍यक्षेत्र माल और सेवा करअधिनियम,2017`
  actYear (2017)
  ministry `Ministry of Finance`
  department `Department of Revenue`
  longTitle `An Act to make a provision for levy and collection of tax on intra-State supply of goods or services or both by the Union territories and for matters connected therewith or incidental thereto.`
  enforcementDate `22nd June, 2017 for sections 1, 2, 3,4,5, 17, 21 and 22. 1st July, 2017 for sections 6 to 16, 18 to 20 and 23 to 26`
  notification `G.S.R. 616(E) dated the 21st June, 2017, Gazette of India, Extraordinary, Part II, sec. 3(i). G.S.R. 701(E) dated the 28th June, 2017, Gazette of India, Extraordinary, Part II, sec. 3(i)`
